# Commit Co-Author Preference

When the user explicitly asks the agent to create a git commit in this
repository, include a `Co-authored-by:` trailer in the commit message by
default.

Use:

`Co-authored-by: OpenAI <noreply@openai.com>`

Only omit the trailer if the user explicitly asks not to include it.
